		<blockquote class="restore">I read through the recordings again instead of just listening to them.<br />
<br />
In writing, there is a clear period in the sentence, but when she reads it, the actress reads it as a comma.  Reading it one way versus the other drastically alters the meaning.  If its a comma, they've run this experiment before.  If it's a period, they've been experimenting on normal infected.</blockquote>
	</div>
</li><li class="postbit blockbody" id="post_11">
